inNumbers.title: Points
inNumbers.description: The combined total number of points scored by both teams throughout the entire match.

inNumbers.title: Duration
inNumbers.description: The total length of the match, from the first serve through until the last point has ended.

inNumbers.title: Spectators
inNumbers.description: Total number of people in attendance at the venue – taken at the end of the second set.

inNumbers.title: Match Spikes
inNumbers.description: The combined total number of successful spikes achieved by both teams throughout the entire match.

inNumbers.title: Reception Level
inNumbers.description: An average of the two team service reception percentages from the complete match.

inNumbers.title: Net Domination
inNumbers.description: The number of successful point winning blocks of VK Dukla LIBEREC compared to Dinamo MOSCOW.

inNumbers.title: Ace Count
inNumbers.description: VK Dukla LIBEREC number of service aces compared to Dinamo MOSCOW

inNumbers.title: Error Difference
inNumbers.description: Errors leading to points of VK Dukla LIBEREC, next to those from Dinamo MOSCOW

info.infoText:
VK Dukla LIBEREC debuted in Champions League only after their 5th season of playing Czech Extralega
Dinamo participatе in the Champions League for a 16th time in a row
Liberec are missing one player, #4 Anna Šotkovská. She got injured in last CL match played in Italy
Dinamo are currently on 4th place in the Russian Superleague counting with 11 wins out of 15 matches
Liberec have won 19 matches out of 22 games and are currently on first place in Czech extraliga
Liberec have already participated in Czech Cup and won a silver medal
Dinamo and Liberec habe met face to face only one time with the result 3-0 for Moscow
